ubject to static and acoustic loads characteristic\nof the launch phase. The paper describes the activities performed and presents\nthe obtained results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Feb 2014 12:02:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 27 Jun 2014 13:39:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 9 Jul 2014 22:18:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
