 of the method of electron gas\ntemperature determination using corrections of the SZ effect due to PRR. Such\nmodification allows one to simplify the determination of the cluster electron\ngas temperature in comparison with known methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Feb 2014 15:45:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Feb 2014 17:01:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
